76
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,330
<i>It was a tectonic shift...</i>

77
00:06:36,329 --> 00:06:40,573
<i>...where everything I thought
I knew about myself got rearranged.</i>

78
00:06:40,867 --> 00:06:44,508
