80
00:06:48,408 --> 00:06:50,354
<i>I felt whole.</i>

81
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:52,421
<i>I'd found my sou! mate.</i>

82
00:06:57,617 --> 00:07:00,257
<i>I couldn't stop smelling his head.</i>

83
00:07:00,420 --> 00:07:02,900
<i>It made me feel drowsy and giddy.</i>

84
00:07:03,056 --> 00:07:06,799
<i>Like we were in the middle of a lavender field
