...what did he say exactly?

147
00:10:44,077 --> 00:10:45,249
Does he talk about us?

148
00:10:45,411 --> 00:10:46,754
No, he was different.

149
00:10:47,147 --> 00:10:50,356
He didn't have normal feelings.

150
00:10:50,984 --> 00:10:52,520
And he smelt like...

151
00:10:52,685 --> 00:10:54,528
...lavender.

152
00:10:55,855 --> 00:10:58,358
You know, like those candles
we have at home.

153
00:11:01,461 --> 00:11:02,496
Yes, dear.

154
00:11:02,762 --> 00:11:04,969
Yes, the change of scenery
was good for Will.

155
00:11:05,131 --> 00:11:06,940
He was getting too stale in New York.

156
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:08,170
Yes, Jess.

157
00:11:08,334 --> 00:11:09,540
