158
00:11:09,702 --> 00:11:11,443
Can you hear me?

159
00:11:11,604 --> 00:11:13,015
Claudia, Claudia--
Jess.

160
00:11:13,173 --> 00:11:15,619
We need to get Mario Testino out here
to do a shoot.

161
00:11:15,775 --> 00:11:17,482
Did you hear that? Jess?

162
00:11:17,644 --> 00:11:19,214
Oh, darn.

163
