220
00:17:22,575 --> 00:17:25,021
No! Please! I'm sorry, I didn't mean it!

221
00:17:25,177 --> 00:17:26,383
Wait. Wait.

222
00:17:26,546 --> 00:17:28,548
Please. I'm sorry.
